cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.PL

This paper is primarily focused on the development of a data pipeline platform built on top of Kubernetes, which is a distributed systems technology. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also discusses the development of software for data sharing circuitry, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). Additionally, the paper discusses the capture of metadata and tracing of provenance, which are topics related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the optimization of energy expenditure and waste, which is related to programming languages and compilers (cs.PL).
